{"tid":1196954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公民黨: 凌晨警民衝突, 林鄭月娥須負全責","createTime":"2019-06-10T00:49:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T01:11:33.000Z","uid":134071,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"58c88e5c5637ac1e48f8a9dd016a55a490f06cc1","tid":1196954,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T00:49:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/civicpartyhk/photos/a.450720993456/10156236891888457/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcivicpartyhk%2Fphotos%2Fa.450720993456%2F10156236891888457%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=OwzbFhxxS8LWxL2ugy7iTFe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=97befe3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/civicpartyhk/photos/a.450720993456/10156236891888457/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n公民黨 Civic Party<br />\n6 小時 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n【公民黨就6月10日凌晨警民衝突事件聲明】<br />\n<br />\n2019年6月9日，有破紀錄的103萬名香港人上街參與遊行、表達對政府《逃犯條例》修訂方案的不滿，及要求林鄭月娥兌現選舉承諾，引咎辭職。<br />\n<br />\n遊行結束後，不少參與者留守立法會外繼續靜坐表達不滿。唯至晚上11時07分，政府發出新聞稿，表示修訂將如常於6月12日於立法會恢復二讀辯論，完全把過百萬香港人的民意視如無物，亦反映了林鄭月娥剛愎自用、目中無香港人的本性。<br />\n<br />\n政府新聞稿發出後，立即激發立法會外參與者的情緒，令原本和平的集會演變成警民衝突，我們認為，政府官員的傲慢、忽視社會重要聲音、以香港的國際聲譽作賭注執意修訂《逃犯條例》，是激起民憤、引致是次衝突的主因，<strong>林鄭月娥必須對事件負上全責。</strong><br />\n<br />\n我們重申，遊行人數已表明反對《逃犯條例》是香港主流民意，特區政府必須撤回修訂；我們亦要求行政長官林鄭月娥立即引咎辭職下台。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨<br />\n2019年6月10日"},{"pid":"314d9a483ce0b9610e70c3e4e33bb3d6d5c4a2c3","tid":1196954,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T00:50:54.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"9649078fa01a4bb9073f0167ee2722926b3bb8dc","tid":1196954,"uid":134071,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T00:52:01.000Z","msg":"公民袋無屌義士? 爆大冷?"},{"pid":"3b511ba19c7477acd0bddbcc5ec08c9b59cfe335","tid":1196954,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T00:53:05.000Z","msg":"公民黨都驚得罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8fd3b29e8fbbae6a2d6b153d91ec68b57572d9b","tid":1196954,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T00:53:36.000Z","msg":"潔癖黨"},{"pid":"19b42cc982c280fa0288bf95e54ea537320c6bc3","tid":1196954,"uid":78039,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"9649078fa01a4bb9073f0167ee2722926b3bb8dc","tid":1196954,"uid":134071,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T00:52:01.000Z","msg":"公民袋無屌義士? 爆大冷?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T00:53:56.000Z","msg":"好似一向冇屌，仲有派律師幫手"},{"pid":"7a22a3abff051609265b7ddaef06cd0857d430b5","tid":1196954,"uid":111898,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T00:58:01.000Z","msg":"依家先黎講　琴晚呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a274b82f6825a26a317372bfa1e17cca57781d14","tid":1196954,"uid":134071,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"7a22a3abff051609265b7ddaef06cd0857d430b5","tid":1196954,"uid":111898,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T00:58:01.000Z","msg":"依家先黎講　琴晚呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T01:08:04.000Z","msg":"6 小時前發文"},{"pid":"7ee7326f67ef0e74112eb431618d52107f13bb71","tid":1196954,"uid":50513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9649078fa01a4bb9073f0167ee2722926b3bb8dc","tid":1196954,"uid":134071,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T00:52:01.000Z","msg":"公民袋無屌義士? 爆大冷?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T01:11:33.000Z","msg":"尋晚見到都好驚訝"}]}